latestIgtvVideos.caption:
I was always a dreamer, since childhood. While many around me told me it's not a good idea to dream so big, my mother and sisters always gave wings to my flight. "Sapne sab hi ke poore hote hai; kisi ke jaldi poore hote hai, toh kisi ke der se, par sapne sab hi ke poore hote hai," they would often tell me.
Today, I am one step closer to my dream. Presenting my first advertisment as a male lead for @blued_india  Thank you guys for always being this kind and affectionate towards me and supporting me. 
Special thanks to @amitkhannaphotography  and @a__square__entertainment  for believing in me ❤️
